the_ war_n in_ the_ former_a republics_n of_ yugoslavia_n is_v forcing_v slovene_a enterprises_n to_ find_v alternative_a trading_a partners_n among_ european_a community_n countries_n as_ a_ means_n of_ compensating_n for_ lost_v markets_n in_ the_ region_n ._ however_r ,_ slovene_a officials_n warn_v that_ capital_n inflows_n will_ not_r increase_v unless_ slovenia_n re-establishes_n trade_n links_n with_ its_ southern_a neighbours_n ._ until_ 1990_ ,_ over_ 30_ per_ cent_n of_ slovenia_n 's_ exports_n were_v with_ the_ former_a yugoslavia_n ,_ while_ about_ 70_ per_ cent_n were_v divided_v between_ comecon_n ,_ the_ now_r defunct_a socialist_a trading_n block_n ,_ and_ western_a european_a countries_n ._ but_ following_v an_ embargo_n by_ serbia_n on_ slovene_a imports_n in_ 1990_ ,_ and_ ensuing_v war_n in_ neighbouring_v croatia_n last_a year_n ,_ slovene_a exports_n to_ the_ former_a yugoslavia_n have_v fallen_v to_ 15_ per_ cent_n of_ that_ previously_r ._ the_ loss_n of_ markets_n in_ the_ former_a yugoslavia_n ,_ and_ the_ war_n ,_ has_v led_v to_ a_ sharp_a drop_n in_ industrial_a production_n ,_ which_ last_a year_n fell_v by_ 15_ per_ cent_n ,_ and_ will_ fall_v a_ further_r 12_ per_ cent_n this_ year_n ._ unemployment_n has_v risen_v to_ 101,000_ ,_ up_ from_ 9_ per_ cent_n to_ 11_ per_ cent_n of_ the_ labour_n force_n ._ however_r ,_ inflation_n is_v falling_v thanks_n to_ a_ strong_a monetary_a policy_n implemented_v by_ slovenia_n 's_ central_a bank_n ._ inflation_n was_v running_v at_ 25_ per_ cent_n a_ month_n last_a october_n ,_ but_ by_ april_ it_ had_v fallen_v to_ 5_ per_ cent_n ._ mr_ feri_n horvath_n ,_ head_n of_ slovenia_n 's_ chamber_n of_ commerce_n ,_ said_v slovenia_n ,_ which_ declared_v its_ independence_n last_a june_n ,_ must_ seek_v new_a markets_n because_ the_ republic_n is_v too_r small_a to_ be_v able_a to_ attract_v large_a amounts_n of_ foreign_a investment_n to_ foster_v growth_n ._ renault_ ,_ french_a car_n manufacturer_n 